{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/Retro_Character_04.png?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bring your game characters to life with <strong>Retro Character Creator Tool</strong>. This easy-to-use tool lets you create 4-directional characters with a wide variety of hair styles, clothing options, and weapon choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>Retro Character Creator Tool</strong> features a user-friendly interface, making it easy for even beginners to create unique and engaging characters for their game. The tool includes a vast library of assets, including hairstyles, clothing, and weapons, all designed in a charming pixel art style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/Retro_Character_01.gif?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character Animations:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Walking: Natural movements to traverse your game world</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Idle: Character stances that breathe life into moments of pause</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attack: Strikes to combat your enemies</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dead: Static dead sprite for impactful in-game consequences</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 Directions (Left, Right, Up, Down)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customizable Colors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compatible with Unity, Godot, GameMaker...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compatible with RPG Maker (VX, MV &amp; MZ)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/Retro_Character_08.gif?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/text_001.png?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/Retro_Character_02.gif?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/Retro_Character_05.gif?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/Retro_Character_06.gif?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Compatibility:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Godot.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">GameMaker.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gdevelop.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RPG Maker VX.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RPG Maker MV. (Battler Included!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">RPG Maker MZ. (Battler Included!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Any engine that uses PNG sprites.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/extras/Retro_Character_07.gif?t=1729885289\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729885289","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291640/page.bg.jpg?t=1729885289","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati